<avg. prec. 1.1> Spes mea Christe Deus, hominum tu dulcis amator, 
<avg. prec. 1.2> Lux, uia, uita, salus, pax et decus omne tuorum, 
<avg. prec. 1.3> Omnia pro quorum uoluisti(==VOLUISTI) ferre salute, 
<avg. prec. 1.4> Carnem, uincla, crucem, uulnus, mortemque, sepulcrum, 
<avg. prec. 1.5> Post tres inde dies deuicta morte resurgens, 
<avg. prec. 1.6> Discipulis uisus, nutantia corda reformans, 
<avg. prec. 1.7> Luce quater dena coelorum summa petisti: 
<avg. prec. 1.8> Viuis in aeternum, nunc et per saecula regnans. 
